- Stack: Electron + TypeScript + Svelte + Tailwind + Vite.
- Processes:
  - Electron Main: `app/main/` → bundles to `dist/main/index.cjs`.
  - Preload: `app/preload/` → secure IPC exposure → `dist/preload/index.cjs`.
  - Renderer: `app/renderer/` → `index.html` → `/src/ts/main.ts` → mounts `@views/App.svelte`.
- Renderer structure:
  - `src/views/` (thin Svelte views)
  - `src/ts/features/<name>/{types.ts,service.ts,store.ts}` (logic, IO, state)
  - `src/components/` (shared UI)
  - `src/styles/` (global styles)
- Aliases:
  - `@renderer/*` → `app/renderer/src/*`
  - `@views/*` → `app/renderer/src/views/*`
  - `@ts/*` → `app/renderer/src/ts/*`
  - `@features/*` → `app/renderer/src/ts/features/*`
  - `@components/*` → `app/renderer/src/components/*`
- Scripts: `npm run dev`, `npm run build`, `npm run typecheck`.
- Docs: see `docs/architecture.md`, `docs/conventions.md`, `docs/howto/*`.

